Package: scryr
Title: Wrapper for Scryfall API
Version: 0.3.2.9000
Authors@R: c(person('Karl', 'Hailperin', email = 'khailper@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut')), person('Colin', 'Fay', role = c('ctb'), comment = c('Wrote generic API code that was the basis of much of the scry_* functions (https://colinfay.me/build-api-wrapper-package-r/)')))
Description: scryr provides R functions to access Scryfall's APIs for card search, sets, and catalogs.
